WEBVTT

00:02:55.813 --> 00:03:00.045
Bio sam veoma, veoma ozbiljno dijete.
(Smijeh)

00:03:00.045 --> 00:03:01.950
I tada,

00:03:01.950 --> 00:03:03.384
ranih 90-ih,

00:03:03.384 --> 00:03:07.214
imao sam svoj veoma revolucionarni
alat:

00:03:07.214 --> 00:03:09.466
faks.

00:03:09.466 --> 00:03:11.644
I faks je bio alat mog aktivizma.

00:03:11.644 --> 00:03:13.202
I u to vrijeme, to je bio najbolji način

00:03:13.202 --> 00:03:15.097
da pošaljete poruku mnogim ljudima

00:03:15.097 --> 00:03:17.535
odjednom.

00:03:17.535 --> 00:03:19.981
Dat ću vam primijer kampanje koju
sam vodio preko faksa.

00:03:19.981 --> 00:03:22.077
Bilo je to uoči Zaljevskog rata,

00:03:22.077 --> 00:03:25.628
organizirao sam globalnu kampanju
potapanja hotela,

00:03:25.628 --> 00:03:27.109
Intercontinentala u Genevi,

00:03:27.109 --> 00:03:28.664
gdje su se James Baker i Tariq Aziz

00:03:28.664 --> 00:03:30.588
našli uoči rata,